  IC Comput(P +* while>0(a,I), Initialize s,1 + LifeSpan(P +* I,Initialize s))
    = IC Comput(P +* I,Initialize s,LifeSpan(P +* I,Initialize s) ) + 3
 holds CurInstr(P +* while>0(a,I),
